The way to declare styles in React Native is the following:

```javascript
var styles = StyleSheet.create({
  base: {
    width: 38,
    height: 38,
  },
  background: {
    backgroundColor: '#222222',
  },
  active: {
    borderWidth: 2,
    borderColor: '#00ff00',
  },
});
```

All the core components accept a style attribute.

